description:
As a User
  I would have correct price after create/edit product in HK prodcut index page, shop product index page and shop product show page
name: Check product price in HK product index page, shop product index page, shop product show page

elements.name: Check no variation product price in HK product index page, shop product index page, shop product show page

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Product Create Page
I pick product photo to product photo selector
I should see delete photo button
I click on info tab
I fill "(dirty data) check HK price 1st product" to english name field
I click on quantity and pricing tab
I fill "20.00" to regular price field
I fill "15.00" to sale price field
I fill "10" to quantity field
I scroll down to breadcrumb
I click on add button
I should see alert
I should be redirected to Product Edit Page
I am on Product Index Page
1st row of product list should contain "check HK price 1st product"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"HK$20.00 HK$15.00 10 (dirty data) check HK price 1st productUnpublishEdit","expectText":"check HK price 1st product"}

steps.name: 1st row of regular price list should contain "HK$20.00"
1st row of sale price list should contain "HK$15.00"
1st row of quantity list should contain "10"
I am on Shop Product Index Page
I input "check HK price 1st product" to search field
1st product of products list should contain 'check HK price 1st product'

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"(dirty data) check HK price 1st productHK$20.00HK$15.00","expectText":"check HK price 1st product"}

steps.name: product strikethrough regular price should contain 'HK$20.00'
product sale price should contain 'HK$15.00'
I click on 1st product of products list
I should be redirected to Shop Product Show Page
Strikethrough regular price should contain 'HK$20.00'
sale price should contain "HK$15.00"
I click on add to cart button
I should see cart panel
cart panel price list should contain "HK$15.00"
I click on checkout button
I should be redirected to Shop Cart Page
row of unit price should contain "HK$20.00"
row of unit price should contain "HK$15.00"
I am on Product Index Page
1st row of product list should contain "check HK price 1st product"
